Class Summary
OADBBaseDAO Base class that all OADB specific DAO classes extend from.
OADBDAOFactory Provides DAO Factory implementation specific for the Oracle Applications Database.
OADBTagDAO Provides implementation of Tag related data access APIs for the Oracle Applications database.
OADBTestDefDAO Provides Data Access API implementations for Oracle Applications Database.
OADBTestRunDAO Provides Oracle Applications Database specific implementations for data access APIs related to Test runs.
OADBTestStatsDAO Provides Oracle Applications Database specific implementations for data access APIs related to Test Statistics.
UTestOADBBaseDAO Test suite for the query APIs in the base DAO.
UTestOADBDAOFactory Contains tests that basically validate that the factory APIs are returning the correct instances of DAO objects.
